OL,3,CPeston: Is it president Burnham?
OL,5,FThe words that come into my head when
OL,6,FI think about Andy Burnham as prime-
OL,7,Fminister-in-waiting are "president"
OL,8,Fand "Boris Johnson".
OL,10,FAs I said on News at Ten on Monday
OL,11,Fnight, his ambition to transfer
OL,12,Fsignificant financial and policy
OL,13,Fpowers from Westminster to the regions
OL,14,F- mayors and local government - would
OL,15,Fweaken the power of his cabinet while
OL,16,Fenhancing his, with his planned
OL,17,FDowning Street North as overseer of
OL,18,Fthis distributed power.
OL,26,@oD@YOUoD@cO]pD@EOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
