PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782821899
OL,3,CPeston: Is it president Burnham?
OL,5,FIn Johnson's case, he capitalised on
OL,6,Fall that to call a snap general
OL,7,Felection, which he won handsomely,
OL,8,Fmore than two years before he needed
OL,9,Fto do so - and it is not far-fetched
OL,10,Fto say that Burnham will also feel the
OL,11,Fsiren call of securing a personal
OL,12,Fmandate from the electorate (whether
OL,13,Fhe executes on that or not).
OL,15,FI don't know whether Johnson is a
OL,16,Fmodel, or a warning or an augury of
OL,17,Fthings to come.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
